longBusinessSummary: Greentech Technology International Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the exploration, development, and mining of tin and copper bearing ores in Australia. It holds 50% interests in the Renison underground mine comprising Renison Bell mine, concentrator, and infrastructure; the Mount Bischoff open cut tin project; and the Renison tailings retreatment project located in Tasmania.
